from\": 1058, \"to\": 1067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was pretty wild how big they were and how talented people were back then, and also how long they preserved them for as long as they have.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"talented people\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can get pretty interested in that kind of stuff just standing there reading the descriptions of all the stuff and the images, and it was definitely a fun few hours.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d So Scheffler got a nice little history lesson.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1409, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.747038177690945e-37, \"text\": \"Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that kind\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"the descriptions\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"all the stuff\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"the images\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"a fun few hours.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"a nice little history lesson\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he could add a gold medal to his second Masters title, the Players Championship and four other wins this year, that would be an impressive bonus.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"his second Masters title\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"the Players Championship\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1535}, {\"ngram\": \"four other wins\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"an i